data.title: Which is the Catholic team in Liverpool?
data.meta_description: Answer (1 of 3): My Father was born in 1907 and was a Liverpool supporter. A mate born later, was certain that Everton was the Catholic club because of the 1930s with so many Irish players. I explained that my Dad, lovely man, but he would never go against the tide and he was a life long Liverpoo...
